calling upon you
again very soon.

496
00:24:11,583 --> 00:24:14,333
I hope you understand.

497
00:24:14,417 --> 00:24:16,250
Please take good care of Subaru.

498
00:24:16,333 --> 00:24:18,083
He's been through a lot.

499
